The negative MR for Sr4(Ru1−xMnx)3O4 (x = 0.34 and 0.41) is different from that seen in the parent compound, which is positive along both the ab plane and c direction prior to the metamagnetic transition field26,27. This confirms that the magnetic properties of Mn-doped system are different from the undoped case. Furthermore, the fact that \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
